# IMS SBC in Kubernetes (DevOps Project)

**9+ Yrs Telecom â†’ DevOps Switch**  
Deploy **Kamailio SBC** in **Kubernetes** with **CI/CD**

## Live Features
- Dockerized SBC
- GitHub Actions CI/CD
- Deployed on Minikube
- Auto-scale + Health checks

![CI](https://github.com/YOUR-USERNAME/ims-devops-sbc/actions/workflows/ci.yml/badge.svg)

---
FROM kamailio/kamailio:latest
EXPOSE 5060/udp
CMD ["kamailio", "-f", "/etc/kamailio/kamailio.cfg", "-D", "-E"]
name: CI/CD for SBC
on: [push]
jobs:
  build:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v3
      - name: Build Docker
        run: docker build -t sbc-ims .
      - name: Test
        run: echo "Build passed!"
Commit changes

